targets.query: SELECT non_negative_difference(mean("errorCount")) FROM "tomcat.GlobalRequestProcessor" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

list.name: Host
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "tomcat_jvm_memory" WITH KEY = "host"

list.label: Aplicación
list.name: WebModule
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "tomcat.Servlet" WITH KEY = "WebModule" WHERE "host" =~ /^$Host$/

list.label: Conector
list.name: Connector
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "tomcat.GlobalRequestProcessor" WITH KEY = "name" WHERE "host" =~ /^$Host$/

list.label: Garbage Collector
list.name: GC
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "tomcat.jvm_garbage_collector" WITH KEY = "name"

list.name: MemoryPool
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES FROM "tomcat.jvm_memory_pool" WITH KEY = "pool_name" WHERE "host" =~ /^$Host$/
